&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Rust, Elixir, or Python in production systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise with distributed databases like ScyllaDB, Cassandra, or similar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise building large scale chat products.&lt;/li&gt;
